    cito:cites <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure5>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure6> ;
    dc:creator "Komai, Tomoyuki; Chan, Tin-Yam; Grave, Sammy De" ;
    dc:title "Chlorotocellidae Komai, Chan & Grave, 2019, fam. nov." ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999> ;
    trt:treatsTaxonName <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Chlorotocellidae> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999>
    bibo:endPage "402" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Zoosystematics and Evolution" ;
    bibo:startPage "391" ;
    bibo:volume "95" ;
    dc:creator "Komai, Tomoyuki; Chan, Tin-Yam; Grave, Sammy De" ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Establishment of a new shrimp family Chlorotocellidae for four genera previously assigned to Pandalidae (Decapoda, Caridea, Pandaloidea)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure5>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure6> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Chlorotocella gracilis Balss, 1914, male (cl 5.0 mm), CBM-ZC 12534. A. Carapace, antennule and antenna, lateral view (left eye removed); B. Anterior part of carapace, lateral view; C. Pleon, lateral view; D. Telson, dorsal view; E. Left eye, dorsal view; F. Left antennular peduncle, dorsal view; G. Left antenna, ventral view; H. Left mandible, outer view; inset, palp, outer view; I. Left maxillule, outer view (coxal endite missing); J. Left maxilla, outer view; K. Left maxilliped 1, outer view; L. Left maxilliped 2, outer view; M. Endopod of left pleopod 1, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314830" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Chlorocurtis jactans (Nobili, 1904), ovigerous female (cl 1.3 mm), CBM-ZC 11596. A. Carapace, lateral view; B. Pleon, lateral view; C. telson, dorsal view; D. Left eye, dorsal view; E. Left antennule, dorsal view (inner flagellum damaged); F. Right antennular peduncle, distal 2 articles, mesial view; G. Left antenna, ventral view (flagellum missing); H. Left mandible, outer view; I. Left maxillule, outer view; J. Left maxilla, outer view; K. Left maxilliped 1, outer view; L. Left maxilliped 2, outer view (epipod broken off)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314833" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Thoracic sternites 6 - 8 and coxae (cx) of pereopods 3 - 5, ventral view. A. Chlorotocus novaezealandiae (Borradaile, 1916), male (17.0 mm), NRIFSF 578 (arrows indicating prominences on sternites 6 - 8); B. Chlorotocella gracilis Balss, 1914, male (cl 4.1 mm), HUMZ-C 1556." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314832" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Chlorotocella gracilis Balss, 1914, male (cl 5.0 mm), CBM-ZC 12534. Left thoracic appendages in lateral view. A. Maxilliped 3; B-F. Pereopods 1 - 5, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314831" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Chlorocurtis jactans (Nobili, 1904), ovigerous female (cl 1.3 mm), CBM-ZC 11596, left thoracic appendages in lateral view (except for C). A. Maxilliped 3; B. Pereopod 1; C. Same, propodus, mesial view; D-G. Pereopods 2 - 5, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314834" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.95.35999.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. A, B. Pandalus montagui Leach, 1814, transitional male (cl 10.5 mm), CBM-ZC 3422; C. Heterocarpus ensifer A. Milne-Edwards, 1881, male (cl 33.0 mm), HUMZ-C 255; D. Chlorotocella gracilis Balss, 1914, male (cl 4.1 mm), HUMZ-C 1556. A. Left antennular peduncle, dorsal view; B. Left mandible, outer view; inset, palp, lateral view; C. Basis of left pereopod 2; D. Basis of right pereopod 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/314835" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

